Mandatory UI rules:
- Desktop-first
- Dark-first, but light-ready architecture
- English UI
- Sidebar-based shell
- Left navigation with collapse/expand
- Grouped navigation
- List page -> object page pattern
- Create/edit on separate pages
- No modal-based document editing
- No inline editing in grids
- No old View/configurator logic
- Checkbox column on all list pages
- Single-column sort only in MVP
- Status badges are informational, not workflow controls

Keep UI dense, structured, and enterprise-style.
Do not introduce consumer-style airy layouts or decorative patterns.
